                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-78-victim600 t18020428-78-viclabel411"></join>: On Sunday night, the 11th of April, about half past eight, the prisoner came in for half a pint of beer, and I saw her pull a curtain back, and take a quart and a pint pewterpot, and brush out of doors very quick; I went out at the door, and caught her by the skirts.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18020428-78-person602">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CHAPMAN
