                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am an officer belonging to Hatton-garden: I was at Mr. Kendall's; he called me, I searched the prisoner, and found a quart pot, and a pint pot, in her apron; I found this piece of metal in her pocket.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I beg for the mercy of the Court. <rs id="t18020428-78-verdict413" type="verdictDescription">
